25
00:02:39,759 --> 00:02:41,039
Because you remind me of myself

26
00:02:41,160 --> 00:02:44,759
when I was young.

27
00:02:54,199 --> 00:02:56,399
When I met my wife Anna,

28
00:02:57,639 --> 00:02:59,080
