62
00:04:57,600 --> 00:04:58,760
I just feel that

63
00:04:59,959 --> 00:05:01,920
you are not like the others to me.

64
00:05:08,040 --> 00:05:09,559
I don't know

65
00:05:09,679 --> 00:05:11,200
