between a man and a woman.

108
00:07:23,959 --> 00:07:25,399
A woman always asks why.

109
00:07:26,559 --> 00:07:27,040
But when a man

110
00:07:27,040 --> 00:07:28,519
falls in love with a woman,

111
00:07:30,600 --> 00:07:31,600
